{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act39side", "eventName": "出蒼白海", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EP-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "見證，征服，定義", "storyInfo": "哈維爾向胡安娜證明自己有能力引導船員們走向另一個未來。棘刺卻在和安納斯塔西奧的對戰中被逼入絕境，跳入正在噴發的蒸汽之中。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g7_olddeck_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "1", "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$calamity_intro", "key": "$calamity_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.5, "xstrength": 25.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我解決了！我把他們都解決了！……溫蒂，你那裡需要幫忙嗎？", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用，我也解決了——只要我剛修好的船別再被撞壞就好！", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#6$2"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！呼……", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstormimpact", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bone_rub", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，我這輩子都不想再去遊樂場坐雲霄飛車了。", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，極境……你身上剛才還沒有這麼多血的！……是剛剛的骸骨碎片嗎？", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "血……？"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "極境", "content": "沒事，為好朋友受點小傷不算什麼。棘刺有了想去做的事情，我要全力支持他才行。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先幫你包紮一下……棘刺他想做什麼？他說過嗎？", "name": "溫蒂"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_400_weedy_1#5$2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎……等時機到了，讓他親口說給你聽！", "name": "極境"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_450_1#11$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g7_olddeck_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，伊西多。你想贖自己的罪，想抹消自己對無辜之人產生的影響，將他們送回原本的生活軌跡。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這究竟是你堅定的意志，還是良心的迴光？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，常有罪人在意識到自己已走上絕路時，慟哭著為他被連累的親友求情……", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這並不代表他真心愧悔。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#2$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個不清楚自己慾望是什麼的人，如何能證明，他有能力抑制慾望，並且抵銷那些釀成的罪過？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。需要抑制慾望的人是你，需要證明自己的人也是你。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……當然，我已說過，慾望無法被殺死。食人的慾望始終活在我的體內，我必須抑制它。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會親手剜下自己的血肉，然後將它棄置。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會證明自己對血肉的渴望能夠被抑制，哪怕只是瞬間。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多清楚地看到，安納斯塔西奧從領口中露出的那些皮膚，都覆蓋著醜陋的疤痕。被剜去又生長出來的血肉，如此難以直視。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說，慾望只會無窮無盡地生長，將越來越多的人拖入深淵。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以此為由，審判過多少人，殺死過多少人？你為什麼偏偏相信自己的慾望能被抑制？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為死亡是一種解脫。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多，在被慾望沾染之前，你還有過正常的生活，行過良善之事。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以在染上慾望之後，你有資格以死解脫。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我的生命，從最初就是一個錯誤，從最初就是一種罪孽。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我若是死去，那我這個可悲的存在，除了褻瀆之外，還能有什麼意義？", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……所以我必須贖罪。在我的慾望發展到無法抑制的地步之前，我會盡我所能地贖罪。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧左手的指甲嵌入自己的胸膛，唯有疼痛才能使他感到一絲安定。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你甚至在乎自己存在的意義。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧，你是真的不配死去，還是太想活著了？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你總在談論自己“食人的慾望”，但你最根深蒂固的慾望，難道不是只有活著而已嗎？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論殘害自己還是審判別人，難道不是只為了讓所謂“罪孽深重”的自己能安心地活著？", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing2", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.7}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.9}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 60.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_cross", "y": 150.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_mid", "y": 150.0, "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_mid", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_fold_hit", "layer": 4.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_mid", "layer": 5.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_cross_hit", "layer": 6.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.2, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧為了聽取伊西多告解而放緩的攻勢，轉瞬間重新變得凌厲。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多每擋下一劍，手臂上的心相原質都會因劇烈的震動，絲絲縷縷地飄浮起來。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不願告解，那就去死吧。", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g8_oldcabin", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attrib