！", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#3$2"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會把錢分給他們每個人，讓他們過更好的生——", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#3$2"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_singleblunt", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hammer", "volume": 0.8, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 35.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝——！", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#4$2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次劇烈的顛簸，哈維爾踉蹌幾步，胡安娜卻借勢躍起，舵輪重重壓在哈維爾身上，血和鹽飛濺起來。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的武器已然斷裂，只能捏緊拳頭，發瘋般地捶打著胡安娜。"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#6$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 5.0, "times": 50.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1579_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝……喝……", "name": "哈維爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1579_1#6$2"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp4"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 35.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾掙扎著從舵輪的重壓下起身，胡安娜一拳將他打回血泊之中。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp2"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 35.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他喘著粗氣，噴著血沫，想要再次起身。胡安娜又是一拳，哈維爾的視野被一片血紅浸透。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾已經沒有半點餘力，他幾乎是在血泊裡掙扎，卻仍一次又一次徒勞地想要站起來。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到他的雙臂、雙腿被舵輪壓到脫臼。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他甚至無法再抬起自己的頭。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我輸了……胡安娜……殺了我吧。", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我……死了之後，不要遷怒剩下的那些船員……是我帶著他們背叛你的。", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你殺了我，一切就結束了吧。", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾看著胡安娜的眼睛。他覺得自己好像從來沒這麼近地直視過她的眼睛，他甚至在裡面看到了自己的倒影。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他突然覺得自己還有些別的話想說。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天……你從我窗前路過……我烤麵包……那是第一次，烤得焦黑……是我失敗了。", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我浪費了珍貴的食物，船員們嫌棄，沒人吃……只有你……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你從窗外路過，抓起一個麵包，慢慢啃著……你邊吃邊露出了滿足的神色……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那一個下午，你把那一整盤都吃光了……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候我在想……為了讓你再露出一絲滿足的笑，我做什麼都願意。", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼都願意……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾閉上眼睛，等待著舵輪軋斷他的脖子。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恭喜你，小哈。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳……咳……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這場新老首領之間的決鬥，你贏了。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#10$2"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，用你全部的力氣站起來，走回去，去找你的船員們。", "name": "胡安娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1581_1#11$2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "哈維爾"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwlstps", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈維爾使出渾身的力氣，想要站起身。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但地上鮮血黏膩，他再也沒有力氣掙扎，他只能緩慢地向前爬行著。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crowdrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1589_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1592_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但一個、兩個，隨後是一群。船員們一個接一個地跑了過來，從血泊中扶起他們奮戰到最後一刻的新首領。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了一場生死與共的拚殺而流出的血淌在一處，他們緊緊地扶著對方。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "57_g7_olddeck_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$corrosion_intro", "key": "$corrosion_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多右臂上的心相原質躍動起來，他向背後劃出一劍，轉身向右閃去。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧立刻緊逼上來，劍鋒直指伊西多的咽喉。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在伊西多預知的方向中，滾燙的蒸汽從船的破洞中噴湧而出，截斷了安納斯塔西奧追擊的步伐。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多重新擺好架勢，他看到安納斯塔西奧那隻被蒸汽灼燒過的手，握劍時沒有絲毫顫抖。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#9$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧不會因蒸汽而退縮，他甚至渴求疼痛。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_swordwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalcollar", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多俯身向蒸汽中刺出一劍。一聲銳響，安納斯塔西奧的長劍應聲落地。"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但下一秒，安納斯塔西奧的手炮已經抵在伊西多的眉心。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "安納斯塔西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1582_1#7$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安納斯塔西奧已然沉默，扣下扳機之前，他不會再言說。"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多被逼得連退幾步，半個身子已在船外。"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說曾經的你只是一個為了活命而掙扎的可憐孩子。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那現在的你，已經在所謂“贖罪”的路上變成了雙手染血的罪人。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，才是你自己最該殺死的人。", "name": "伊西多"}, "figure_art": "avg_1039_thorn2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多縱身一躍。"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_gunsingle", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$tactfulboost", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "57_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "57_i10", "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手炮發射的聲響迴盪在峽谷中，迴響在中空的骨骸之中。"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多看見安納斯塔西奧將手炮收回腰間，然後像重獲新生般閉上雙眼。"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多轉頭看到身下黑漆漆的空洞。骨骸中的熱流與他手臂上的心相原質一齊湧動，他知道自己即將被蒸汽吞沒。"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但最後，他望向天空。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越過高聳的骨骸，透過蒸汽掀起的熱浪，他看見那雲與天，就如同傳聞中泛著白色浪花的湛藍汪洋。"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是他想要親眼見證的大海。"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊西多向蒸汽的噴發孔墜去。"}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 0.9, "channel": "3", "delay": 0.8}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "4", "delay": 1.5}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "5", "delay": 2.5}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_steamburst_big", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "6", "delay": 2.9}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}